headline: Allstate (ALL) Forms 'Hammer Chart Pattern': Time for Bottom Fishing?
summary: After losing some value lately, a hammer chart pattern has been formed for Allstate (ALL), indicating that the stock has found support. This, combined with an upward trend in earnings estimate revisions, could lead to a trend reversal for the stock in the near term.
